Hello! I'm ready to help you search and explore your codebase. I'm operating in READ-ONLY mode, which means I can:

✓ Search for files using glob patterns
✓ Search through file contents using grep
✓ Read and analyze files
✓ Run read-only bash commands (ls, find, cat, git status, etc.)

I cannot modify, create, or delete any files.

What would you like me to search for or explore in your codebase at `/home/stanner/Downloads`?
